      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "REDBACK JACK (1) turned in a solid run last start over 390m at this track finishing 4th and beaten only 5 lengths (21.95). Form here at the trip sound including three wins. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Can bounce back. GOLDSTAR RODNEY (8) turned in a modest effort most recently when eighth at this track over 352m behind Flying Jilliby (20.63) in a Grade 5. Placed at his previous run. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Has ability and can atone. MELISSA'S FLYING (2) produced a moderate performance last time when fifth at Q Straight over 350m behind HAYDEN'S GIFT (19.37) in a Grade 5. Smart beginner who should take advantage of the low draw. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. HAYDEN'S GIFT (7) good strike-rate overall and must be included.",
